NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Test::Rinci - A release test for Rinci metadata

VERSION
    version 0.01

DESCRIPTION
    This is an extension of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::InlineFiles, providing the
    following files:

      xt/release/rinci.t - a standard Rinci metadata test

    This test uses Test::Rinci to check your Rinci metadata.

ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS
    Code based on Dist::Zilla::Plugin::PodCoverageTests by RJBS.

